Matthew 28-11 <pb/>While they were going, behold, some of <f>ⓞ</f>the guard went into the city and told the chief priests all that had taken place.
Matthew 28-12 And when they had assembled with the elders and taken counsel, they gave a sufficient sum of money to the soldiers
